A cyberpunk-style digital illustration of two distinct neon-lit server towers facing each other across a dark void, connected by streams of glowing data particles that must pass through a floating translucent barrier between them. The barrier pulses with electric blue energy, selectively allowing some data streams through while deflecting others that scatter into red sparks. The towers have intricate circuit-board patterns etched into their surfaces, emanating warm orange and cool cyan glows. The scene is set against a deep purple-black cityscape horizon with distant holographic grid lines. Rain falls through the scene, creating reflective puddles below that mirror the light show above. The composition emphasizes the tension between connection and restriction, with the barrier as the focal point where approved and rejected data streams visually diverge.
